Orange Crush, is a  12 x 12 x 2”  MM Collage and Painting on stretched linen. 

Recorded and mixed in West Seattle (Duwamish-Land) January, 2022 by Marc Fendel @fendelmarc musiceducationforall.com Instruments: Selmer Super Balanced alto saxophone serial number #36868 1948, Vital Synthesizer, Slick EQ, Black Wave Table VCO by Erica Synths, Interzone Valley, Interzon Plateau reverb, VCF Bog Audio, Random Sampler, Mix 8- Bog Audio, VCV Rack 2, Elektron Model Samples, & Reaper DAW.
